flowchart LR
    %% A typical CI/CD Pipeline
    Developer([Developer]) -->|git push| GitHub(GitHub Repo)
    
    subgraph CI [Continuous Integration]
        GitHub -.->|webhook| Actions{GitHub Actions}
        Actions --> Build[Build App]
        Actions --> Test[Run Tests]
        Actions --> Lint[Lint Code]
        
        Build --> Docker[(Docker Image)]
        Test --> Result((Pass or Fail))
    end
    
    subgraph CD [Continuous Deployment]
        Docker ==> Deploy[Deploy to Staging]
        Deploy --> E2E[E2E Tests]
        E2E -->|success| Prod[Deploy to Production]
    end
    
    Result -.->|status| Developer
